data.description: An immaculately maintained custom home, that is TURN KEY!!! Many features include vaulted ceilings, an open concept kitchen with title floors, granite and hickory cabinets throughout the home, Hardwood floors, carpet flooring in the bedrooms. 2 primary suites, one with a private deck. Large deck that overlooks the mountains and property. An abundance of large windows throughout the home allows for great views & lots of natural light. Relax or entertain on the many decks with beautiful views of the mountains.
